s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe5665966a1d927295eca4690222d0f377d69ecf","tid":958490,"uid":2470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"死左都未知咩事<br />\n一個唔該染埋愛滋 細菌感染等等<br />\n唔抵可憐"},{"pid":"d327b9e2955ab25b6503a0867bc24ab892eb3cd2","tid":958490,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce1952da35040c70aae7a6cd7f5c5c532f3861a0","tid":958490,"uid":181527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你信唔信搵<span style=\"color: red;\">個</span>咁既醫生整完出嚟會有靚女？</blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:17:48.000Z","msg":"信呀，班大陸整容西咪又係咁整，撇開衞生安全風險，呢d咪又係手工野，醫生手勢未必好過美容師"},{"pid":"499ebc7def14d81c88ebd35f72a7984e3c4030b4","tid":958490,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:24:25.000Z","msg":"嘥氣、有邊個國家唔係咁既趨勢？香港已經跟得慢<br />\n有得J你就J啦"},{"pid":"720451a1b421c2402f26d046c69a0dd468c80708","tid":958490,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e844346ed1aed964ff16c432629aafebac16f154","tid":958490,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得多左靚仔就真<br />\n雖然好多廋到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得少左喎<br />\n20歲樓下個堆D頭柒撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55229a0be0978e2bd01053fcd8b8443237c1a57a","tid":958490,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"720451a1b421c2402f26d046c69a0dd468c80708","tid":958490,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e844346ed1aed964ff16c432629aafebac16f154","tid":958490,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T01:02:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得多左靚仔就真<br />\n雖然好多廋到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:08:41.000Z","msg":"我反而覺得少左喎<br />\n20歲樓下個堆D頭柒撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"支那樣<img src=\"/as